name: Vrundavan Packaging
overview: Founded in the year 2008, we, “Vrundavan Packaging”, are a widely acclaimed manufacturer, exporter and supplier of a broad gamut of Corrugated Box, Corrugated Roll, Corrugated Carton and Mini Corrugated Box. The range we deal in comprises Printed Corrugated Box, Corrugated Tool Box, LID Corrugated Box, Heavy Duty Corrugated Box, Corrugated Paper Box and Corrugated Cardboard Box. In addition to this, we also bring forth various types of HP Corrugated Roll, Corrugated Sheet Roll, Drain Cardboard Box, E-Flute Box, Corrugated Chocolate Box, HDPE Corrugated Box, Corrugated Crunch Box. These boxes and rolls are made using pristine quality paper, corrugated fiber board and paper board and that too in exact compliance with the defined packaging standards and guidelines.
